item.title: Products
item.dc:creator: user
item.content:encoded:
Every Good Meadow product is lovingly baked with a sense of warmth and old world tradition. Handcrafted by artisan bakers in small batches, our wholesome breads and treats are made from time-honored, family recipes using only the finest ingredients. And because our bakery is 100% peanut-free, everyone can enjoy Good Meadow with peace of mind.
From our signature White House Rolls<sup>®</sup> to our famous Rainbow Cookies<sup>TM</sup>, each bite evokes memories of time spent with family – a time when life was a little simpler. It’s an ideal we hope to pass onto your family today and for generations to come.

item.title: Home Page
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded:
A New Brand Built on a Longstanding Tradition

When the Ukrop family came to the United States from the Slovak village of Dobrá Niva (meaning “Good Meadow”) over 100 years ago, they brought with them a tradition of gathering everyone around the table to share a daily meal. This tradition was first honored at our family’s grocery store, where founders Joseph and Jacquelin Ukrop routinely served homemade meals to employees. Their commitment to freshly-made foods later became the cornerstone of Ukrop’s prepared foods business. Today, we’re building upon this tradition by introducing our newest brand: Good Meadow Homemades. Good Meadow captures what our family has learned about food over the last quarter century. We offer you our favorite recipes, freshly prepared with wholesome ingredients, to enjoy again and again as you gather your family around the table, too.

item.title: White House Rolls
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded:
Our soft and tasty White House Rolls<sup>®</sup> have been a household staple for generations. Both our original recipe and wholesome wheat version are made from scratch and shaped by hand. These rolls were so named because of the flour dusted on top—and, because we think they’re good enough to be served at The White House!
You can enjoy our original and wheat White House Rolls by the dozen or try our convenient 6-count or 2-count package. They are great right out of the bag or warmed in the oven – perfect for sandwiches, dinner rolls, snacking and more. And with no preservatives and zero trans fats, you can feel good about sharing them with your whole family.

item.title: Crème Cakes
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded: Bring home one of our deliciously moist crème cakes and watch everyone’s eyes light up! Try the lemon version, chock full of tangy citrus flavor and glazed with a luscious lemony sauce. Or dig into a slice of our chocolate fudge crème cake, made with rich cocoa then topped with a creamy chocolate fudge icing.

item.title: Pies
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded:
There’s nothing quite like a slice of homemade pie fresh from the oven. We offer three delicious flavors – rich Chocolate Fudge, zesty Lemon Chess and traditional Southern Pecan – to share with the whole family. From our flaky, made-from-scratch crust to the highest quality ingredients, we don’t cut corners with our pies. Just big slices.
Try our pies for holidays, special occasions, or as a sweet treat for your family. With our traditional recipes and premium ingredients, they’ll never know you didn’t bake it yourself.

item.title: Cornbread
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded:
Cornbread has been a Southern tradition for as long as we can remember. We make ours from scratch using a traditional family recipe and only the best ingredients. Finely textured with a delicate, sweet flavor, our cornbread is the perfect complement to a hearty meal. Many people love it as a snack by itself!
In addition to our Sweet flavor, try Jalapeno Cheddar for a spicy kick. Both have zero grams of trans fat, making them wholesome options you can feel good about sharing.

item.title: Tarts
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded:
We took everything you love about our homemade pies and put them into single servings, perfect for a quick, on-the-go snack. Our tarts are made from the same traditional recipes with the same made-from-scratch crust. They’re also available in three delicious flavors – rich Chocolate Fudge, zesty Lemon Chess and traditional Southern Pecan.
Can’t decide on a favorite? These pint-sized treats make it easy to mix and match for everyone in your family.

item.title: Rainbow & Butterstar Cookies
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded:
You’ll feel like a kid again when you bite into our famous Rainbow Cookies<sup>TM</sup> or sweet Butterstar Cookies. Soft and buttery, these tiny treats are made from scratch using our traditional cookie recipes and premium ingredients. Add a splash of color and they’re just as fun as they are delicious.
Good Meadow cookies are a natural favorite for kids, making them great for snacks and lunch boxes. Although, we know quite a few adults who pack them in their own lunch boxes, too.

item.title: Biscuits
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded: There’s nothing better than a tender, flaky biscuit. Bite into one of our made-from-scratch buttermilk biscuits that taste just like Grandma’s. Perfect with a dab of butter or jam. Or try our Cheese Biscuits packed with tangy cheddar cheese for an unforgettable flavor. Either one you choose will be a delicious addition to breakfast, lunch or dinner. Warm them in the oven or microwave for the most satisfying taste!

item.title: Sandwiches, Salads & Sides
item.dc:creator: tfuqua
item.content:encoded: Make your own fresh and healthy meal with a combination of Good Meadow sandwiches, salads and sides. Enjoy a gourmet sandwich, like a Chicken Salad Croissant, Slow Roasted London Broil on Focaccia or Pimento Cheese on a famous White House Roll. Keep it light with a Cobb Salad or delicious sides like Redskin Potato Salad or freshly cut Watermelon, Cantaloupe and Pineapple. Each sandwich, salad and side is made daily by our family, so you can share it with yours!
